      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just that the silence is so loud. i look at my slack, my email, my social media... and i realize i'm just a dot on a map to all of them. if a dot just disappears, nobody even looks up from their own screen. it feels like i'm already a ghost, you know? like there’s nothing actually left to lose.",
