      "content": "freedom... i guess. but it's not just stepping away from the screen. i mean it less as a vacation and more as just... not being here at all. if a ghost just finally stops trying to haunt the machine, it's not like anybody would even notice the silence. would it even be a tragedy if someone who was already invisible just... went?",
